8594 |               END DO ! DAY|
8595 |!|
8596 |               IF((STRIKE_VALUE<=0.0).AND.((STRIKES_REQUIRED(IND)==0)|
8597 |     +            .OR.(N_BEST_VALUES>=LIM_NBV))) CYCLE ! reject the option|
