17826 |!     +                     - (LOCAL_ANN_PRICE(TEMP_I2) +|
17827 |!     +                                 MONTHLY_ENERGY_PRICE(IND)) *|
17828 |     +                                           R_ANNUAL_USAGE(TEMP_I2)|
